1. **Game Reset Functionality**
JavaScript function to reset the game board:

```javascript
function resetGame() {
  const cells = document.querySelectorAll('.tic-tac-toe-cell');
  cells.forEach(cell => {
    cell.textContent = ''; // Clear content
    cell.classList.remove('X', 'O'); // Clear player classes
  });
  currentPlayer = 'X'; // Reset starting player
}

// Attach this function to a reset button
document.querySelector('.reset-button').addEventListener('click', resetGame);
```

